Ok lets come to conclusion whether arjun reddy is better or kabir singh is better. Acting:- VJD( Shahid actually did better but tbh VJD was natural and shahid just enacted) Fight:- shahid( The fight scenes in kabir singh was actually good or better than arjun reddy) Heroine:- Kiara Advani ( Sorry Shalini, kiara simply nailed it) Story:- Both are same so its common. Lov scenes:- Kabir scene(Arjun reddy love scenes where great but few scenes were to much. Whereas in kabir singh scenes are beautifully done)   Role of shiva:- sorry both have done great job Emotion:- Shahid( Even tho VJD was first to do that, Shahid has that natural emotions because he himself is a love failure so many emotional scenes were great in kabir singh. Dialogues:- Arjun reddy( Man those intense dialogues were goosebumps. Editing:- Both were long movie so its equal. Location and light pattern:- both are good, but kabir singh location and light pattern were really good. Attitude:- VJD( man this guy has got serious attitude was actually natural than shahid). Supporting role:- Both movie supporting role was outstanding but one on arjun reddy was marginally good. Songs and music:- (both were great but kabir singh songs were too addicted and good to hear) Getup and stylish- VJD(man this guy so adaptive to that character. Overall kabir singh -6              Arjun Reddy-5 Since Arjun reddy is 2 years old film, the director has fullfil all the gaps which he left in arjun reddy. So an extra mark to Arjun reddy for shadowing extra details kabir singh and also this was a remake. Verdict conclusion  Kabir singh 6 Arjun reddy 6. Both are great in their perspective. So hatsoff to both of them and cant deny both justify their role. Thankyou and have great day.
